code: @Before public void setUp() {     this.webSocketHandler = mock(WebSocketHandler.class).     this.taskScheduler = mock(TaskScheduler.class).     this.sockJsConfig = new StubSockJsServiceConfig().     this.sockJsConfig.setTaskScheduler(this.taskScheduler).     this.session = initSockJsSession(). }
protected void assertNew() {     assertState(true, false, false). }
protected void assertOpen() {     assertState(false, true, false). }
protected void assertClosed() {     assertState(false, false, true). }

private void assertState(boolean isNew, boolean isOpen, boolean isClosed) {     assertEquals(isNew, this.session.isNew()).     assertEquals(isOpen, this.session.isOpen()).     assertEquals(isClosed, this.session.isClosed()). }
